{
  "id": 5201048700583936,
  "name": "CSS anchor positioning with transforms",
  "summary": "When an anchor-positioned element is tethered against an anchor that has a transform (or is contained by something with a transform), resolve anchor() and anchor-size() functions against the bounding box of the transformed anchor.",
